#################################################################################################################################################
								IRIO EPICS Sample Unit
#################################################################################################################################################
=================================================================================================================================================
IRIO EPICS Sample Unit description:
=================================================================================================================================================
The IRIO EPICS Sample Unit tests the complete integration of advanced data acquisition applications in EPICS using IRIO technology. 
It allows the users to test five different applications.
These applications are:
-cRIOIO: Application based on cRIO platform using direct I/O data acquisition profile.
-cRIODMA: Application based on cRIO platform using DMA data acquisition profile.
-fRIO5761: Application based on flexRIO platform (PXIe7966/65+NI5761) using DMA data acquisition profile.
-fRIO6581: Application based on flexRIO platform (PXIe7966/65/61+NI6581) using DMA data acquisition profile.
-fRIO1483: Application based on flexRIO platform (PXIe7966/65+NI1483) using Image DMA data acquisition profile.

In the following website, users can find all info needed about IRIO Technology.

Website: http://www.i2a2.upm.es/idi/instrumentacion-aplicada/sistemas-de-adquisicion-de-datos-avanzados-2/irio-technology/



=================================================================================================================================================
IRIO EPICS Sample Unit hardware and software needs:
=================================================================================================================================================
IRIO EPICS Sample Unit needs:
Hardware:
-cRIO Platform: 
	-Chassis: NI9159
	-I/O Modules: NI9264, NI9205, NI9401, NI9477, NI9426, NI9476,and NI9425.
-flexRIO Platform: 
	-Chassis: PXI Express chassis compatible with NI RIO Linux driver 15.0 and compatible with PXIe79xx FPGAs family.
	-FPGAs: PXIe7966, PXIe7965 and/or PXIe7961
	-Adapter Modules: NI5761, NI6581 and/or NI1483
Software:
	-NI-RIO Linux Driver 
	-EPICS Base
	-SynApps (Busy, Sscan, Autosave and Calc)
	-IRIO Library
	-IRIO EPICS Device Support

In the following website, users can find all info needed about how to install required software packages in a ScientificLinux distribution.

WebSite: http://www.i2a2.upm.es/idi/instrumentacion-aplicada/sistemas-de-adquisicion-de-datos-avanzados-2/irio-software-tools-installation/



